'''MBBA'''，即'''N-(4-甲氧基苯亞甲基)-4-丁基苯胺'''（{{lang-en|N-(4-Methoxybenzylidene)-4-butylaniline}}），是一種[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]，屬於[[亞胺|亞胺]]類，含有[[醚|醚]]、[[苯|苯]]、醛亞胺和[[醚|醚]]等[[官能基|官能基]]，具有[[液晶|液晶]]相態，且[[常溫|常溫]]下就呈液晶態<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://webbook.nist.gov/cgi/cbook.cgi?ID=C26227736&Mask=4|title=Phase change data|accessdate=2013-12-05|publisher=webbook.nist.gov|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017193829/http://webbook.nist.gov/cgi/cbook.cgi?ID=C26227736&Mask=4|archive-date=2018-10-17|dead-url=yes}} webbook.nist.gov [2013-12-5]</ref>，是一種研究较多的液晶材料，其[[化學式|化學式]]為C<sub>18</sub>H<sub>21</sub>NO<ref>[http://webbook.nist.gov/cgi/cbook.cgi?InChI=InChI%3D1/C18H21NO/c1-3-4-5-15-6-10-17(11-7-15)19-14-16-8-12-18(20-2)13-9-16/h6-14H%2C3-5H2%2C1-2H3/b19-14%2B%0A MBBA-NIST Webbook] {{Wayback|url=http://webbook.nist.gov/cgi/cbook.cgi?InChI=InChI%3D1%2FC18H21NO%2Fc1-3-4-5-15-6-10-17%2811-7-15%2919-14-16-8-12-18%2820-2%2913-9-16%2Fh6-14H%2C3-5H2%2C1-2H3%2Fb19-14%2B%0A |date=20181017193829 }} webbook.nist.gov [2013-12-5]</ref>。

==性質==
MBBA的在[[常溫|常溫]]下為[[液晶|液晶]]態，[[凝固點|凝固點]]為22度<ref name="Shinoda, Maeda, et al., 1974">Shinoda, T.; Maeda, Y.; Enokido, H., Thermodynamic properties of N-(p-methoxybenzylidene)-p-n-butyl-aniline (MBBA) from 2K to its isotropic-liquid phase, J. Chem. Thermodynam., 1974, 6, 921-934.</ref>，[[熔點|熔點]]為47度<ref>Shinoda, T.; Mizuno, M., On the pre-transition phenomenon of n-(p-methoxybenzylidene)-p-n-butylaniline (MBBA), Tokyo Kogyo Shikensho Hokoku, 1982, 77(4), 215-217.</ref>，22到47度為液晶相<ref>John Wiley & Sons,Optics of Liquid Crystal Displays Pochi Yeh, Claire Gu ,2010 ,ISBN 0470181761,第16頁</ref><ref>Wiley Series in Pure and Applied Optics第 67 卷, ISSN 0277-2493</ref>。從[[固態|固態]]變成液晶態的相變熱為ΔH<sub>trs</sub>=15.9377 kJ/mol、ΔS<sub>trs</sub>=53.91 k/mol K；從液晶相變成液相的相變熱為ΔH<sub>trs</sub>=0.2841 kJ/mol、ΔS<sub>trs</sub>=0.89 k/mol K<ref name="Shinoda, Maeda, et al., 1974"/>；[[熔化熱|熔化熱]]為ΔH<sub>trs</sub>=18.033 kJ/mol、ΔS<sub>trs</sub>=61.04 k/mol K<ref>Janik, J.A.; Janik, J.M.; Mayer, J.; Sciesinska, E.; Sciesinski, J.; Twardowski, J.; Waluga, T.; Witko, W., Calorimetric and infrared study of the phase situation in solid MBBA [N-(p-methoxybenzylidene)-p-(n-butyl)aniline], J. Phys. (Paris) Colloq., 1975, (1), 159-165.</ref>，[[三相點|三相點]]約為[[攝氏|攝氏]]20度<ref>Janik, J.A.; Janik, J.M.; Mayer, J.; Sciesinska, E.; Sciesinski, J.; Twardowski, J.; Waluga, T.; Witko, W., Calorimetric and infrared study of the phase situation in solid MBBA [N-(p-methoxybenzylidene)-p-(n-butyl)aniline], J. Phys., Colloq., 1975, 1, 159</ref>，另外，固、液、液晶共存為295.3 K，約為22.15 °C<ref>TRC - Thermodynamics Research Center, NIST Boulder Laboratories, M. Frenkel director</ref>。

MBBA不溶於[[水|水]]、異氰酸酯、鹵代有機物、[[過氧化物|過氧化物]]、[[酚類|酚類]]（[[酸性|酸性]]）、環氧化物、[[酸酐|酸酐]]和鹵化物，與氫結合可能生成強還原劑，如氫化物。<ref name="look-chemical"/>

MBBA為長條型[[液晶|液晶]][[分子|分子]]，[[常溫|常溫]]下會以間列式（線條式，或稱為[[向列型液晶|向列型]]，nematic phase）的方式排列。<ref name="LCY"/>

